data.description: Come home to this meticulously maintained property in the sought after community of Sandy Plains Estates in East Cobb. Its open concept main floor features plenty of natural light and a newly painted interior, large kitchen and dining room overlooking the fireside family room. The owners suite, two large bedrooms and one full bathroom completes the main floor. The oversized deck, freshly painted and maintained, overlooks the large, private backyard that is perfect for entertaining on those long, hot,  summer nights, including separate, private wooded area including with a treehouse slide and bistro lighting throughout the trees, and separate, side level yard off the deck.  A new favorite meeting place for friends and family.  The finished lower level features two large finished bedrooms and a full bathroom and large double garage.  This large home offers so, so much, including close proximity to sought after schools and restaurants, I75, Barrett Parkway shopping and the new Sprayberry Crossing currently under construction.
